{"tid":1385700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該你地要買眼罩既全部買透明 咪撚再買有顏色","createTime":"2019-07-30T06:51:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T07:44:28.000Z","uid":260934,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"631ba93742d8e9f4437fe39bb0628238a327aa69","tid":1385700,"uid":260934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:51:26.000Z","msg":"話說小妹知自己體能廢 每次發夢都係中後排嗌下口號 傳下物資 收下情報咁 但728個晚眼見咁多位師兄師姐明明有gear都唔上前 吹水先知原來<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">普通眼罩唔夠擋/泳鏡黑色睇唔到野</span></span>所以上唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁多位奶爸奶媽 哥哥姐姐 <br />\n唔該你地要大手入貨既就買<span style=\"color: red;\">透明泳鏡</span> 費事一陣好心做壞事 成班人一到夜晚就盲烏蠅咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"97b076d0f833fef0fcef4117ed814644f5ca0f86","tid":1385700,"uid":260934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:51:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8bce58cfd0880095e05fafcdb69881be39021118","tid":1385700,"uid":260934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:52:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0157f63dfa39dc56a7006c4777cec60b0e3da7ec","tid":1385700,"uid":164938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:52:38.000Z","msg":"Fact checked<br />\n明天機場博覽館要人！！<br />\n7.31<br />\n16:00-17:30<br />\n機場Asia World Expo-Summit 2號展館<br />\n政府開pre policy address meeting! <br />\n會議是為運輸及貿易界而設既諮詢會，將有好多公司出席！<br />\n<br />\n聽日7.31機場博覽館要人！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385635\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385635</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ccdfe3fd2ca0a469e20cb1873aac7f20ea2da00e","tid":1385700,"uid":55257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tCLK4sE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtCLK4sE.png&h=d2ec08fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國務院已批出和平遊行集會<br />\n<br />\n呼籲各位8月4日再次上街遊街、8月5日罷工集會，我們再一次重申對特區政府的五大訴求：<br />\n<br />\n一、徹底撤回逃犯條例修訂<br />\n二、收回612暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、成立獨立調查委員會追究警隊濫權<br />\n五、立即實行真正的雙普選<br />\n<br />\n我們熱愛香港，不願再有香港人為守護家園而流血，甚至犠牲寶貴性命。<br />\n<br />\n但我們強調&mdash;&mdash;「沒有暴民，只有暴政」，我們誓必以一切方法迫使政府完全正面回應並實現我們的訴求。<br />\n<br />\n我們促請政府盡快回心轉意，使香港重回正軌，成為團結、民主、自由、公義的社會。<br />\n<br />\n8.4 將軍澳<br />\n13:30<br />\n寶翠公園&mdash;&mdash;&gt;單車館公園<br />\n<br />\n8.4 港島西<br />\n16:00<br />\n科士打臨時遊樂場&mdash;&mdash;&gt;中山紀念公園<br />\n<br />\n8.5 全民罷工七區集會<br />\n13:00<br />\n沙田、荃灣、屯門、黃大仙、大埔、旺角、金鐘<br />\n<br />\n和理非全面上場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"132c64f222e3831fc26aa864e2f858c122b5d60b","tid":1385700,"uid":1392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:53:17.000Z","msg":"夢想做工程師或者汽車維修員既同學仔入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383220</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫手推"},{"pid":"9bb46eac52ae8ed35167c270bf719abb4006b2a3","tid":1385700,"uid":260934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:53:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2620d64f7e138b087a3a83ce19b04531487a540","tid":1385700,"uid":260934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:55:11.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"f21aaac8d30188f324cbb5ae677013843344e3f1","tid":1385700,"uid":210140,"like":